    <entry>
      <title>递归思想实现搜索</title>
      <link href="/2024/03/11/recursion/"/>
      <url>/2024/03/11/recursion/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1>递归思想实现搜索</h1><h2 id="斐波那契数列">斐波那契数列</h2><h6 id="斐波那契数列-是一组-有序数列-满足">斐波那契数列 是一组 有序数列 满足</h6><p>$$<br />a(n + 1) = a(n)  + a(n - 1)<br />$$</p><h6 id="代码实现">代码实现</h6><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">fb</span>(<span class="params">n</span>):</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> n == <span class="number">1</span> :</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">elif</span> n == <span class="number">2</span> :</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> fb(n - <span class="number">1</span>) + fb(n - <span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(fb(<span class="number">5</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>时间复杂度: O(2^n)</p><p>空间复杂度：n</p></blockquote><h2 id="递归实现指数型枚举">递归实现指数型枚举</h2><h6 id="在1-n-个数字中，任意取多个，列出所有的组合">在1 ~ n 个数字中，任意取多个，列出所有的组合</h6><blockquote><p>方法1：</p><p>​生成 1 到 n 的数组</p><p>​取数组中没一位数添加到新的数组中去</p><p>​每次添加都是一个新的组合</p><p>​在新的数组中从第二个开始移出数组，又是一个新的组合</p></blockquote><h6 id="代码实现-2">代码实现</h6><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">tb</span>(<span class="params">lon</span>):</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>( )</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> j,i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">enumerate</span>(<span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">1</span>,lon + <span class="number">1</span>)):</span><br><span class="line">ls = []</span><br><span class="line">ls.append(i)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(i)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> n_n <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(j + <span class="number">2</span>,lon + <span class="number">1</span>):</span><br><span class="line">ls.append(n_n)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> d <span class="keyword">in</span> ls:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(d,end = <span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;\t&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="built_in">len</span>(ls) &gt;= <span class="number">3</span>:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> n <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="built_in">len</span>(ls)-<span class="number">1</span>):</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">del</span> ls[n]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> num <span class="keyword">in</span> ls:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(num,end = <span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;\t&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">tb(<span class="number">3</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>方法2：</p><p>​创建数组存放每个位置数据的状态，0 表示未考虑，1 表示选中，2表示不选</p><p>​根据状态生成结果</p></blockquote><h6 id="代码实现-3">代码实现</h6><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">n = <span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line">st = []</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> xxxx <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(n):</span><br><span class="line">st.append(<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">dfs</span>(<span class="params">x</span>):</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># x 表示判断的位置</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> x &gt;= n:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(n):</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> st[i] == <span class="number">1</span>:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(i + <span class="number">1</span>,end = <span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;\t&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 不选</span></span><br><span class="line">st[x] = <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">dfs(x + <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">st[x] = <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 选中</span></span><br><span class="line">st[x] = <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">dfs(x + <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">st[x] = <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">dfs(<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="递归实现排列型枚举">递归实现排列型枚举</h2><blockquote><p>题目:</p><p>对 n 个数字进行排序</p><p>输出排列方式</p><p>输入： 3</p><p>输出：</p><p>1 2 3</p><p>1 3 2</p><p>2 1 3</p><p>2 3 1</p><p>3 2 1</p><p>3 1 2</p></blockquote><h6 id="代码实现-4">代码实现</h6><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nu = <span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line">ne = []</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> xxxx <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(nu):</span><br><span class="line">ne.append(<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">sort_n</span>(<span class="params">n</span>):</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> n &gt;= nu:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="built_in">len</span>(<span class="built_in">set</span>(ne)) == <span class="number">3</span>:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 去掉重复的数组</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(nu):</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(ne[i],end = <span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;\t&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ne[n] = <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">sort_n(n + <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">ne[n] = <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ne[n] = <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">sort_n(n + <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">ne[n] = <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ne[n] = <span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line">sort_n(n + <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">ne[n] = <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">sort_n(<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h6 id="优化标记">优化标记</h6><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">n = <span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line">st = []</span><br><span class="line">arr = []</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(n):</span><br><span class="line">st.append(<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">arr.append(<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">sort_nus</span>(<span class="params">i</span>):</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> i &gt;= n:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># print(123)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> nud <span class="keyword">in</span> arr :</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(nud,end = <span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;\t&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> cd <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">1</span>, n + <span class="number">1</span>):</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> st[cd - <span class="number">1</span>] == <span class="literal">False</span>:</span><br><span class="line">st[i] = <span class="literal">True</span></span><br><span class="line">arr[i] = cd</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(cd)</span><br><span class="line">sort_nus(i + <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">st[i] = <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">arr[i] = <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># print(123)</span></span><br><span class="line">sort_nus(<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="递归实现组合型枚举">递归实现组合型枚举</h2><blockquote><p>从 n 个元素中抽出 r 个元素进行组合列如输入n = 5 ，r = 3<br />输出:<br />123/124/125…</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 还没有写好，等待中</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="总结">总结</h2><h6 id="上面的编程过程中涉及了DFS的思想">上面的编程过程中涉及了DFS的思想</h6><h6 id="列入第一题中的思路如下">列入第一题中的思路如下</h6><p><img src="https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/beforelike/picx-images-hosting@master/image.67x7n8b8ga.png" alt="递归实现搜索" /></p>]]></content>
      
      
