    <entry>
      <title>矩形切割</title>
      <link href="/2024/02/27/%E7%9F%A9%E5%BD%A2%E5%88%87%E5%89%B2/"/>
      <url>/2024/02/27/%E7%9F%A9%E5%BD%A2%E5%88%87%E5%89%B2/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<hr /><h2 id="问题描述">问题描述</h2><p>小有一些矩形的材料，他要从这些矩形材料中切出一些正万形。当他面对一块短形材料时，他总是从中间切割一刀，切出一块最大的正万形，剩下一块矩形，然后再切割剩下的矩形材料，直到全部切为正方形为止。例如，对于一块两边分别为5和3的材料（记为5x3),小明会依次切出3x3,2x2,1x1,1x1共4个正方形。现在小明有一块矩形的材料，两边长分别是2019和324.请问小明最终会切出多少个正方形？<br /> <br /><br />##分析：<br /><br /><img src="https://beforelike.github.io/picx-images-hosting/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE-2024-02-28-134954.86tdvweuh7.webp" alt="" /></p><h2 id="代码实现">代码实现</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">lenth = <span class="number">5</span></span><br><span class="line">raw = <span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line">n = <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span> lenth != raw:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">lenth = lenth - raw</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> lenth &lt; raw:</span><br><span class="line">lenth, raw = raw, lenth</span><br><span class="line">n += <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(n + <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="总结">总结</h2><p>将边与边一直相减下去，每减一次就相当于在矩形上剪下来一个正方形。由于两边不等，所以最后肯定会剩余两个边长为1的正方形。最后加上。</p>]]></content>
      
      
